    <lb n="3"/>ἐνεστῶτος <num value="3">γ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> ἀμφοδογραμματέως Αὐρηλίου Σαραπίωνος εἰς ἐπιτήρη<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>ιν ὠνῆς <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.93">πελ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ωχικ</unclear>οῦ</lem><rdg>πελ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ωχ</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ου</rdg></app> πόλεως 

